snippet.title: Crash Course Builder - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2382630/Crash_Course_Builder

Announcing Crash Course Builder, an intense, quick twitch, rhythm racer filled with screen rattling explosions and hilarious rag doll physics.

Coming soon on Steam, Xbox, Playstation, Switch, iOS & Android.

Visit http://www.crashcoursebuilder.com to find out more.
